data.description: Welcome to this STUNNING 3-story Grayslake townhome with 2 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, featuring a captivating POND VIEW from the front door and living room windows. The main level welcomes you with a spacious living room, dining area, and a bright kitchen with a PRIVATE BALCONY. Adjacent is the attached LAUNDRY ROOM for added convenience. Upstairs, two roomy bedrooms include a primary bedroom with a WALK-IN CLOSET and PRIVATE FULL BATH, complemented by a second full bath on the same floor. The English basement offers a bonus room, storage space, and access to the attached 2-CAR GARAGE. The HOA manages all exterior maintenance, providing a hassle-free lifestyle. ***UPDATES INCLUDE: Professional home & carpet cleaning (Feb 2024), New Stove/Oven (fall 2023), New A/C unit (2022), & New Washer & Dryer (fall 2021).*** View the Virtual 3D Tour to preview the home easily.
